<br>
I've got no problem with spreading the healing duties around if they give clerics something else to do and one ... just one ... &quot;class defining skill&quot; (which I thought was rez and complete heal, then thought was complete heal, now I'm not so sure.)<br>
<br>
In the meantime, if they actually give a cleric enough soloing power to take down a barely-blue that isn't undead, I might see it as a fair trade. Tag on a couple of utilities (such as a way to regenerate mana -- whether from stealing it, bleeding it, gathering it, or whatever -- and for god sakes, please, a normal freakin' invisibility) and I'd be a happy cleric.<br>
<br>
But the news from test leaves me feeling less than enthusiastic.  <p>Faithfully yours,<BR><BR>


