LORE, MAGIC, NO DROP, NO RENT<br>
AC 10<br>
14 DMG, 18 DLY, Bane Undead +10<br>
25 Dex, 8 Wis, 35 HP, 35 Mana<br>
+ 10 Sv. Disease, + 5 Sv. Magic, +10 Sv. Poison<br>
Effect: Hand of the Gods.<br>
