<br>
I'm sorry if this was a little in-depth but its what needs to be said...  Look at this from a CLERICS point of view, not a ROGUE (Zera) sorry but you just dont know what your saying... Take away CH from clerics? Sure, VI can take our CH when they take a rogue's BACKSTAB! Hey while we're at it how bout Enchanter's MEZ, say Druid's ports and snare, Shaman slows, monk FD, and how bout mage's pets?!  Sound like a fun to you?  For godsakes man wtf are you thinking?!?!<br>
